 Regional buying volume
 Preparedness readiness
 Property protection actions
 Youth exchange participation
 Businesses supported
 Total aid distributed
 Total reserves
 Reports completed
 Leadership vacancies
 Conflict/repair cases
 Privacy incidents
 Member satisfaction
 Local autonomy concerns
The dashboard should ask:
Are roots getting stronger?
Are societies more capable?
Are reports more consistent?
Are privacy and dignity protected?
Are resources moving downward?
Is federation support helping local societies?
